9117e47f-6c55-4819-82e4-bb0ae93720da/5435-1
00:42:21.535 --> 00:42:22.545
<v Lina Čeponienė>arba šakes, arba abu.</v>

9117e47f-6c55-4819-82e4-bb0ae93720da/5449-0
00:42:24.295 --> 00:42:27.364
<v Lina Čeponienė>Gerai tai dabar,
